807
00:53:28.708 --> 00:53:30.833
Look. I've been tryin' to stop him.
but I can't.

808
00:53:31.333 --> 00:53:34.041
The only person
he would ever listen to is my mom.

809
00:53:34.708 --> 00:53:37.916
- Can you tell me about her?
<i>- She…</i>

810
