<i>♪ Don't they know… ♪</i>

974
01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:52.416
Your business with me is done.

975
01:07:59.416 --> 01:08:00.583
Shah's dead.

976
01:08:01.291 --> 01:08:03.291
Hmm. Shah didn't hire me.

977
01:08:04.291 --> 01:08:07.791
My contract is to take out anyone
who can implicate my employer.

978
01:08:10.416 --> 01:08:11.666
Who else are you hunting?

979
01:08:14.666 --> 01:08:16.583
Only the one sitting next to me.

980
01:08:21.333 --> 01:08:23.125
Something for you. darling?

981
01:08:23.875 --> 01:08:24.875
No.

982
01:08:35.375 --> 01:08:36.875
I know your struggle.

983
01:08:38.250 --> 01:08:39.250
I do.

984
01:08:41.333 --> 01:08:43.041
The village I grew up in.

985
01:08:43.625 --> 01:08:45.000
we were farmers.

986
01:08:46.458 --> 01:08:48.458
I worked in the fields with my father.

987
01:08:49.500 --> 01:08:51.625
And one day. a group of rebels came.

988
01:08:53.083 --> 01:08:57.125
They slaughtered my entire village.
Everyone. Whole family. friends.

989
01:08:58.625 --> 01:09:00.583
I was able to hide in the weeds.

990
01:09:01.083 --> 01:09:03.916
Now. you gotta understand.
I was just a kid. know that?

991
01:09:04.750 --> 01:09:08.125
In such pain. with such… rage

992
01:09:08.208 --> 01:09:11.125
that for years. I hunted them one by one.

993
01:09:12.083 --> 01:09:14.500
- Then you understand.
- [hit man] I do.

994
01:09:16.500 --> 01:09:18.333
You see. what I've learned in that process

995
01:09:18.416 --> 01:09:21.958
is that there will always be
an opposing force.

996
01:09:22.666 --> 01:09:24.875
No amount of revenge can change that.

997
01:09:25.666 --> 01:09:26.750
[sighs]

998
01:09:27.875 --> 01:09:30.375
So you see. in this case.

999
01:09:31.958 --> 01:09:33.625
you are my village.

1000
01:09:34.458 --> 01:09:36.583
and I am the opposing force.

1001
01:09:44.666 --> 01:09:45.666
[Ray smacks lips]

1002
01:09:46.791 --> 01:09:49.000
[sighs]

1003
01:09:49.083 --> 01:09:50.958
<i>♪ Don't they know… ♪</i>

1004
01:09:52.375 --> 01:09:55.541
[clicks tongue]
Well. there's three ways this goes down.

1005
01:09:57.458 --> 01:10:00.291
One. I tell those cops who we are

1006
01:10:01.500 --> 01:10:03.833
and this gets real ugly for both of us.

1007
01:10:06.458 --> 01:10:07.458
Two.

1008
01:10:08.250 --> 01:10:10.000
I walk out the front door.

1009
01:10:10.083 --> 01:10:13.041
spend the rest of my life hiding
in the four corners of this earth.

1010
01:10:13.625 --> 01:10:15.250
and neither of us get what we want.

1011
01:10:17.958 --> 01:10:18.958
Or three.

1012
01:10:20.458 --> 01:10:22.125
you tell me who hired you.

1013
01:10:23.208 --> 01:10:25.250
We both know I'm gonna go after them.

1014
01:10:25.916 --> 01:10:27.500
And when I do.

1015
01:10:28.666 --> 01:10:30.666
you can try to take another shot at me.

1016
01:10:32.208 --> 01:10:33.333
This way.

1017
01:10:33.958 --> 01:10:35.875
at least one of us gets what we want.

1018
01:10:43.458 --> 01:10:44.458
Nah.

1019
01:10:45.500 --> 01:10:47.875
No. you've killed a few men. but…

1020
01:10:48.833 --> 01:10:51.250
Their deaths are still fresh in your eyes.

1021
01:10:53.250 --> 01:10:55.291
You're a dilettante in my world.

1022
01:10:56.791 --> 01:10:58.458
I never set out to kill anyone.

1023
01:10:59.458 --> 01:11:00.750
Not like you.

1024
01:11:01.750 --> 01:11:03.500
You are not innocent.

1025
01:11:05.208 --> 01:11:08.208
You knew going after powerful people
was a dangerous business.

1026
01:11:09.458 --> 01:11:10.625
You jumped.

1027
01:11:11.125 --> 01:11:13.416
I'm just the pavement closing in.

1028
01:11:17.750 --> 01:11:19.500
[sighs deeply]

1029
01:11:19.583 --> 01:11:20.875
Diana Morgan.

1030
01:11:21.916 --> 01:11:23.500
The person you're looking for.

1031
01:11:24.625 --> 01:11:25.666
[Ray clears throat]

1032
01:11:26.458 --> 01:11:27.458
The senator.

1033
01:11:29.875 --> 01:11:31.375
See you in Pittsburgh.

1034
01:11:33.666 --> 01:11:35.666
[ominous music playing]

1035
01:11:45.666 --> 01:11:46.791
Rachel.

1036
01:11:50.125 --> 01:11:51.416
I'll see ya soon.

1037
01:12:13.750 --> 01:12:15.750
[indistinct chatter]

1038
01:12:26.250 --> 01:12:28.791
Rothman. you have kids.

1039
01:12:29.375 --> 01:12:31.041
Does the idea of Rachel Cooper

1040
01:12:31.125 --> 01:12:34.166
being dragged through all of this
bother you at all?

1041
01:12:35.083 --> 01:12:38.500
Every case we work has me worried
about my kids one way or another.

1042
01:12:39.333 --> 01:12:41.041
I keep thinking about her.

1043
01:12:43.875 --> 01:12:44.875
I mean. how's…

1044
01:12:45.375 --> 01:12:48.750
How's a kid supposed to get past
all that she's seen?

1045
01:12:54.416 --> 01:12:55.458
I feel like…

1046
01:12:56.083 --> 01:12:58.958
I feel like I need to protect her somehow.

1047
01:13:01.708 --> 01:13:04.000
- Just do the work...
- [agent] Memo came through.

1048
01:13:04.083 --> 01:13:06.166
- Search crew found Cooper's vehicle.
- Where?

1049
01:13:06.250 --> 01:13:08.958
[agent] In the woods.
20 miles outside Shah's compound.

1050
01:13:11.041 --> 01:13:12.958
Looks like local PD got a call
this morning

1051
01:13:13.041 --> 01:13:15.666
that a tow truck was stolen
at a nearby location.

1052
01:13:15.750 --> 01:13:17.791
We need eyes
on all street cameras on Route 8.

1053
01:13:17.875 --> 01:13:19.375
- [agent] I'm on it.
- Thank you.

1054
01:13:30.333 --> 01:13:33.375
Okay. Fort Pitt Tunnel.
Only 12 minutes away.

1055
01:13:38.875 --> 01:13:40.875
[somber music playing]

1056
01:13:43.541 --> 01:13:45.083
[phone ringing]

1057
01:13:46.250 --> 01:13:47.583
War room.

1058
01:13:49.416 --> 01:13:52.458
Hey. guys. We got a hit on that tow truck.
It's headed back to the city.

1059
01:13:52.541 --> 01:13:55.458
- [suspenseful music playing]
- [helicopter blades whirring]

1060
01:13:55.541 --> 01:13:58.208
[dispatcher 1. on radio] <i>Suspect is</i>
<i>in a red tow truck. 10-80.</i>

1061
01:13:58.291 --> 01:14:00.958
<i>License plate Romeo Tango One Seven</i>

1062
01:14:01.041 --> 01:14:02.750
<i>Uniform Alpha Sierra.</i>

1063
01:14:02.833 --> 01:14:06.625
[officer 1] <i>We may have something here.</i>
<i>Westbound on Liberty passing 16th.</i>

1064
01:14:09.625 --> 01:14:11.583
[Rachel] The chopper! It's on us.

1065
01:14:12.125 --> 01:14:15.541
[officer 1] <i>We've got eyes on the suspect.</i>
<i>Making a right turn on 9th.</i>

1066
01:14:17.375 --> 01:14:20.083
<i>North on 9th. Picking up speed.
Making a run for it.</i>

1067
01:14:20.166 --> 01:14:21.458
All right. Hold on. baby.

1068
01:14:22.000 --> 01:14:23.375
[Rachel] Oh shit!

1069
01:14:23.458 --> 01:14:24.958
[panting]

1070
01:14:25.041 --> 01:14:27.791
[officer 2. over speaker]
<i>Police! Stop the vehicle now!</i>

1071
01:14:27.875 --> 01:14:29.666
- [engine revs]
- [Rachel] Whoa!

1072
01:14:29.750 --> 01:14:31.333
- [screams]
- [tires squeal]

1073
01:14:35.500 --> 01:14:38.000
- Where's the chopper?
- It's on your right. On your right.

1074
01:14:40.083 --> 01:14:41.333
[officer 2] <i>Pull over.</i>

1075
01:14:42.708 --> 01:14:45.208
[tow truck engine revving]

1076
01:14:46.458 --> 01:14:47.583
- Whoo!
- [Rachel] No!

1077
01:14:48.750 --> 01:14:50.583
- Get outta the way!
- [people scream]

1078
01:14:54.375 --> 01:14:55.625
Oh shit!

1079
01:14:57.000 --> 01:14:58.333
[horns blaring]

1080
01:15:01.250 --> 01:15:03.916
- God damn it! Hold on. Hang on!
- [Rachel screams]

1081
01:15:12.958 --> 01:15:15.791
[dispatcher 1. on radio] <i>All units.</i>
<i>suspect is armed and dangerous.</i>

1082
01:15:15.875 --> 01:15:18.041
<i>I repeat. armed and dangerous.</i>

1083
01:15:18.125 --> 01:15:19.791
[horns blaring]

1084
01:15:19.875 --> 01:15:21.916
[Ray] The game's letting out.

1085
01:15:22.000 --> 01:15:23.333
[quietly] Oh shit!

1086
01:15:23.416 --> 01:15:25.250
[sirens approaching]

1087
01:15:35.708 --> 01:15:38.791
- [dispatcher 2] <i>Got eyes on the suspect.</i>
- [officer 3] On the move!

1088
01:15:38.875 --> 01:15:40.708
[suspenseful music playing]

1089
01:15:41.958 --> 01:15:43.625
[Ray panting]

1090
01:15:44.708 --> 01:15:46.750
[Meeker and Rothman panting]

1091
01:15:56.208 --> 01:15:59.041
[officer 4. on radio] <i>Suspect on foot.</i>
<i>I repeat. suspect on foot.</i>

1092
01:16:02.041 --> 01:16:04.666
[indistinct radio chatter]

1093
01:16:07.708 --> 01:16:10.125
[dispatcher 2]
<i>Suspect is entering PNC Park.</i>

1094
01:16:10.208 --> 01:16:11.541
[indistinct chatter]

1095
01:16:13.666 --> 01:16:16.041
- [man 1 grunts]
- [man 2 grunts] Hey!

1096
01:16:16.125 --> 01:16:17.500
[woman 1] What?

1097
01:16:18.000 --> 01:16:20.600
- [Meeker] Everybody clear. FBI!
- [Rothman] Move! Out of the way!

1098
01:16:32.791 --> 01:16:34.631
[Meeker] If he's down here.
we squeeze him out.

1099
01:16:34.708 --> 01:16:36.208
I'll take the upper level.

1100
01:16:36.291 --> 01:16:39.083
PPD. cover this level.
The rest. go upstairs.

1101
01:16:49.541 --> 01:16:51.625
[crowd shouting]

1102
01:16:56.583 --> 01:16:58.666
- [officer 5] Suspect spotted.
- [crowd cheering]

1103
01:17:15.500 --> 01:17:16.916
Suspect spotted on the upper level.

1104
01:17:24.166 --> 01:17:25.166
[people grunt]

1105
01:17:37.583 --> 01:17:39.625
Get me agents to the roof. now!

1106
01:17:42.833 --> 01:17:44.833
[Meeker panting]

1107
01:18:24.500 --> 01:18:26.500
[helicopter blades whirring]

1108
01:18:31.083 --> 01:18:32.250
[Rothman] Move!

1109
01:18:33.041 --> 01:18:34.166
[officer 6 grunts]

1110
01:18:36.958 --> 01:18:38.791
- [officer 7] I got eyes on.
- [Rothman] Copy.

1111
01:18:41.291 --> 01:18:43.291
[helicopter blades whirring overhead]

1112
01:18:55.000 --> 01:18:56.000
[Meeker] Wait!

1113
01:18:56.458 --> 01:18:57.541
Wait.

1114
01:18:58.500 --> 01:19:00.625
Okay. [gasps]

1115
01:19:03.958 --> 01:19:07.458
It wasn't right what happened to you.
I understand that.

1116
01:19:08.875 --> 01:19:11.041
Look. no one is gonna hurt you.

1117
01:19:11.625 --> 01:19:13.708
It's me. I'm here to help.

1118
01:19:13.791 --> 01:19:14.958
Okay?

1119
01:19:15.041 --> 01:19:17.791
- [somber music playing]
- I don't know you.

1120
01:19:18.458 --> 01:19:20.083
Yes. you do. We've…

1121
01:19:21.250 --> 01:19:22.625
We've been talking.

1122
01:19:26.958 --> 01:19:28.625
No. Paloma.

1123
01:19:29.750 --> 01:19:32.791
You told me
your stuffed bunny's name was Paloma.

1124
01:19:33.791 --> 01:19:36.083
[Ray exhales deeply]

1125
01:19:37.000 --> 01:19:38.166
Remember?

1126
01:19:44.708 --> 01:19:46.791
It wasn't supposed to be like this.

1127
01:19:48.333 --> 01:19:50.250
[Meeker] Your father was a good man.

1128
01:19:50.333 --> 01:19:52.166
[train rattling on tracks]

1129
01:19:54.833 --> 01:19:56.541
[Meeker] <i>You are not him.</i>

1130
01:19:57.041 --> 01:19:59.041
[somber instrumental music building]

1131
01:20:00.833 --> 01:20:01.833
[extinguisher hisses]

1132
01:20:01.875 --> 01:20:03.333
- [Rachel grunts]
- [thwacks]

1133
01:20:03.416 --> 01:20:04.416
[Keeley groaning]

1134
01:20:04.500 --> 01:20:06.708
[choking and grunting]

1135
01:20:07.833 --> 01:20:08.833
[Rachel grunts]

1136
01:20:09.666 --> 01:20:12.708
[exhales. breathing shakily]

1137
01:20:14.041 --> 01:20:15.041
[gasps]

1138
01:20:18.250 --> 01:20:20.500
[Rachel grunting. echoing]

1139
01:20:22.125 --> 01:20:23.125
[panting]

1140
01:20:23.166 --> 01:20:25.333
- [Meeker] <i>Say your name.</i>
- [Rachel gasps]

1141
01:20:26.166 --> 01:20:28.083
[Meeker] <i>You are in control.</i>

1142
01:20:29.583 --> 01:20:30.708
[firing rapidly]

1143
01:20:32.125 --> 01:20:33.125
[sighs] Fuck.

1144
01:20:33.208 --> 01:20:35.458
You're nothing but a scared little...

1145
01:20:35.541 --> 01:20:36.916
- [gunshot]
- [Rachel grunts]

1146
01:20:38.041 --> 01:20:40.250
[panting]

1147
01:20:42.875 --> 01:20:43.958
[hit man] Rachel.

1148
01:20:44.750 --> 01:20:46.291
I'll see ya soon.

1149
01:20:46.375 --> 01:20:48.041
[echoing] Say your name.

1150
01:20:49.791 --> 01:20:50.916
[Ray. echoing] <i>Rachel.</i>

1151
01:20:51.541 --> 01:20:53.250
We're gonna be okay.

1152
01:20:54.541 --> 01:20:57.208
[somber music swells]

1153
01:20:59.125 --> 01:21:01.083
[Meeker] He shouldn't have been killed.

1154
01:21:03.250 --> 01:21:06.541
Come on. just… say… your name.

1155
01:21:06.625 --> 01:21:07.833
[Rachel gasps]

1156
01:21:17.333 --> 01:21:18.791
[Meeker] Just say your name!

1157
01:21:26.666 --> 01:21:28.000
Rachel Cooper.

1158
01:21:28.083 --> 01:21:30.083
- [music fades]
- [wind whistling]

1159
01:21:31.791 --> 01:21:32.916
Yeah.

1160
01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:35.517
[dispatcher 2] <i>We have</i>
<i>a positive identification of the suspect.</i>

1161
01:21:35.541 --> 01:21:36.958
<i>Her name is Rachel Cooper.</i>

1162
01:21:41.291 --> 01:21:43.208
[tense music playing]

1163
01:21:44.958 --> 01:21:47.041
No. No. no. no. Rachel!

1164
01:22:01.875 --> 01:22:04.083
[music fading]

1165
01:22:04.166 --> 01:22:07.000
- [sirens wailing]
- [helicopter blades whirring overhead]

1166
01:22:08.416 --> 01:22:10.416
[indistinct radio chatter]

1167
01:22:20.875 --> 01:22:22.416
[Meeker] <i>Her name is Rachel Cooper.</i>

1168
01:22:23.000 --> 01:22:24.541
<i>Eighteen years of age.</i>

1169
01:22:25.916 --> 01:22:28.041
[paramedic] <i>Any family to contact?</i>

1170
01:22:28.125 --> 01:22:30.333
[Meeker] <i>Both parents deceased.</i>

1171
01:22:30.416 --> 01:22:32.416
[siren wailing]

1172
01:22:34.625 --> 01:22:36.625
[Rachel breathing heavily. echoing]

1173
01:22:40.541 --> 01:22:41.958
[grunts softly]

1174
01:22:49.125 --> 01:22:50.125
[grunts]

1175
01:22:54.041 --> 01:22:56.583
[gasping]

1176
01:23:01.333 --> 01:23:02.916
[grunts]

1177
01:23:03.000 --> 01:23:04.458
- [yells]
- [paramedic groans]

1178
01:23:04.541 --> 01:23:06.083
[Rachel grunting]

1179
01:23:07.166 --> 01:23:08.458
- [grunts]
- Okay. calm down!

1180
01:23:10.375 --> 01:23:11.875
- [Rachel chomps]
- [Meeker] Fuck!

1181
01:23:11.958 --> 01:23:12.875
[groans]

1182
01:23:12.958 --> 01:23:14.208
[Rachel groans]

1183
01:23:14.291 --> 01:23:16.250
[dramatic instrumental music playing]

1184
01:23:22.708 --> 01:23:23.875
[brakes screech]

1185
01:23:26.458 --> 01:23:28.250
[Rachel groaning]

1186
01:23:28.333 --> 01:23:29.458
[driver] No!

1187
01:23:30.833 --> 01:23:32.208
- [Rachel grunts]
- [tires squeal]

1188
01:23:35.708 --> 01:23:37.125
[Meeker] Rachel. stop!

1189
01:23:37.708 --> 01:23:39.750
- [Rachel grunts]
- [music fades]

1190
01:23:41.500 --> 01:23:43.083
[sounds muffled]

1191
01:23:52.666 --> 01:23:53.791
[Rachel grunts]

1192
01:23:53.875 --> 01:23:55.375
[glass shards clink]

1193
01:23:55.458 --> 01:23:57.666
- [siren wailing in distance]
- [Rachel grunts]

1194
01:23:57.750 --> 01:24:00.375
- [panting]
- [somber music playing]

1195
01:24:01.708 --> 01:24:02.833
[Meeker groans softly]

1196
01:24:09.833 --> 01:24:10.916
[Rachel grunts]

1197
01:24:11.000 --> 01:24:13.000
[panting]

1198
01:24:13.083 --> 01:24:15.250
[sirens wailing in distance]

1199
01:24:21.291 --> 01:24:23.625
[shakily] <i>♪ She's got a smile ♪</i>

1200
01:24:25.541 --> 01:24:27.750
<i>♪ That it seems to me ♪</i>

1201
01:24:30.583 --> 01:24:33.875
<i>♪ Reminds me of childhood ♪</i>

1202
01:24:36.291 --> 01:24:38.791
<i>♪ Memories ♪</i>

1203
01:24:40.500 --> 01:24:45.291
<i>♪ Where everything was as fresh ♪</i>

1204
01:24:45.375 --> 01:24:49.250
<i>♪ As the bright blue sky ♪</i>

1205
01:24:51.208 --> 01:24:52.208
[gasps]

1206
01:24:56.875 --> 01:24:58.166
There you are.

1207
01:25:01.125 --> 01:25:02.125
[sighs]

1208
01:25:08.250 --> 01:25:09.666
I'm scared.

1209
01:25:16.583 --> 01:25:19.791
I feel like the whole world's gone crazy.

1210
01:25:19.875 --> 01:25:20.958
[sniffles]

1211
01:25:23.791 --> 01:25:25.583
Or maybe it's just me.

1212
01:25:31.666 --> 01:25:33.208
I'm tired.

1213
01:25:36.666 --> 01:25:37.750
[takes a deep breath]

1214
01:25:38.583 --> 01:25:41.000
Nobody cares about stopping them.

1215
01:25:41.958 --> 01:25:43.708
Besides me.

1216
01:25:56.416 --> 01:25:59.291
Will I ever get to see you and Mom again?

1217
01:25:59.375 --> 01:26:00.416
[sniffles]

1218
01:26:01.416 --> 01:26:02.875
[softly] We're with you now.

1219
01:26:02.958 --> 01:26:04.958
[Rachel crying softly]

1220
01:26:14.708 --> 01:26:15.833
[sniffles]

1221
01:26:29.500 --> 01:26:31.500
[tense music playing]

1222
01:26:33.291 --> 01:26:34.458
[Rachel sighs]

1223
01:26:38.333 --> 01:26:40.916
[Morgan] The fight begins here.

1224
01:26:41.000 --> 01:26:43.250
[crowd cheering]

1225
01:26:44.708 --> 01:26:46.833
Big business and corporate interests

1226
01:26:46.916 --> 01:26:48.833
have corroded our politics.

1227
01:26:48.916 --> 01:26:50.666
[crowd boos]

1228
01:26:50.750 --> 01:26:54.250
[Morgan] And I believe that our country
is on the verge of imploding.

1229
01:26:55.208 --> 01:26:56.208
Of rotting.

1230
01:26:56.250 --> 01:26:58.416
Rotting from the inside out.

1231
01:26:58.500 --> 01:27:00.166
[crowd jeers]

1232
01:27:00.250 --> 01:27:03.041
[Morgan] We need someone who will clean…

1233
01:27:03.125 --> 01:27:05.000
[Morgan and crowd] …out the rot!

1234
01:27:05.083 --> 01:27:07.416
- Clean out the rot!
- [crowd cheers]

1235
01:27:10.791 --> 01:27:13.708
Today. I am announcing my bid

1236
01:27:13.791 --> 01:27:15.333
to be your next senator

1237
01:27:15.416 --> 01:27:17.791
from the great state of Pennsylvania.

1238
01:27:17.875 --> 01:27:19.250
[crowd cheers]

1239
01:27:19.333 --> 01:27:20.791
[chuckles] That's right.

1240
01:27:22.583 --> 01:27:24.333
[tense music building]

1241
01:27:24.416 --> 01:27:26.791
And to big business politics.

1242
01:27:27.666 --> 01:27:29.541
we have one thing to say.

1243
01:27:30.458 --> 01:27:31.916
This is our state.

1244
01:27:32.500 --> 01:27:35.833
and it is not for sale!

1245
01:27:35.916 --> 01:27:38.458
[crowd cheering]

1246
01:27:41.458 --> 01:27:44.500
[camera shutters clicking]

1247
01:28:16.291 --> 01:28:18.083
[horn beeps]

1248
01:28:59.583 --> 01:29:00.708
[staffers exclaim]

1249
01:29:02.208 --> 01:29:03.250
[staffer] Well done.

1250
01:29:03.333 --> 01:29:05.750
Entering the race is just the beginning.

1251
01:29:05.833 --> 01:29:08.541
Let's focus on what we wanna do
when we win.

1252
01:29:08.625 --> 01:29:10.541
[staffers chattering]

1253
01:29:12.083 --> 01:29:13.333
[door creaks]

1254
01:29:13.416 --> 01:29:15.416
[somber music playing]

1255
01:29:57.833 --> 01:29:59.833
[gentle music playing]

1256
01:29:59.916 --> 01:30:01.916
[Rachel breathing shakily]

1257
01:30:07.041 --> 01:30:08.750
- [sighs]
- [Ray] <i>Where'd you get this?</i>

1258
01:30:11.083 --> 01:30:12.916
- It's Mom's.
- [Ray chuckles]

1259
01:30:13.416 --> 01:30:14.875
Actually. it's mine.

1260
01:30:15.958 --> 01:30:19.000
<i>I took your mom to a Steelers game
shortly after we met.</i>

1261
01:30:19.083 --> 01:30:21.541
and it was freezing.
and I gave her my jacket.

1262
01:30:21.625 --> 01:30:23.083
And she never gave it back.

1263
01:30:26.750 --> 01:30:28.916
Well. now it's my turn
to steal it from her.

1264
01:30:30.000 --> 01:30:31.000
[Ray] Hmm.

1265
01:30:31.083 --> 01:30:33.125
[Rachel]
<i>It's my turn to steal it from her.</i>

1266
01:30:34.041 --> 01:30:35.208
[Rachel sighs]

1267
01:30:37.708 --> 01:30:38.916
[exhales slowly]

1268
01:30:57.083 --> 01:30:59.083
[energetic music playing]

1269
01:31:11.166 --> 01:31:12.208
[key reader beeps]

1270
01:31:33.541 --> 01:31:35.208
[blade swishes]

1271
01:31:35.291 --> 01:31:36.891
- [tense music playing]
- [Rachel grunts]

1272
01:31:38.166 --> 01:31:39.333
[hit man groans]

1273
01:31:43.458 --> 01:31:44.750
[Rachel panting]

1274
01:31:48.041 --> 01:31:50.333
[grunting]

1275
01:32:12.333 --> 01:32:13.750
- [loud banging]
- [Rachel groans]

1276
01:32:21.250 --> 01:32:22.916
- [gun fires]
- [Rachel gasps]

1277
01:32:27.500 --> 01:32:28.875
[boards creak overhead]

1278
01:32:30.083 --> 01:32:31.291
[Rachel gasps]

1279
01:32:33.291 --> 01:32:34.708
[boards creaking]

1280
01:32:34.791 --> 01:32:36.291
[boards creak overhead]

1281
01:32:45.875 --> 01:32:47.708
[Rachel gasps. panting]

1282
01:33:24.458 --> 01:33:27.166
- [both grunting]
- [gun firing]

1283
01:33:27.250 --> 01:33:28.500
[gun clatters]

1284
01:33:29.125 --> 01:33:30.833
[Rachel groans]

1285
01:33:30.916 --> 01:33:32.166
[grunts. yells]

1286
01:33:32.250 --> 01:33:34.083
[suspenseful music playing]

1287
01:33:34.791 --> 01:33:35.791
[Rachel gasps]

1288
01:33:37.833 --> 01:33:39.041
[blade swishes]

1289
01:33:42.083 --> 01:33:43.625
- [blade clicks]
- [Rachel grunts]

1290
01:33:43.708 --> 01:33:44.875
[groans]

1291
01:33:47.833 --> 01:33:49.333
- [blade slices]
- [Rachel screams]

1292
01:33:49.875 --> 01:33:51.000
[yelling]

1293
01:33:52.208 --> 01:33:53.250
[screams]

1294
01:33:55.166 --> 01:33:56.333
[blade swishes]

1295
01:33:56.416 --> 01:33:58.416
- [Rachel yells]
- [hit man groans]

1296
01:34:00.458 --> 01:34:02.333
- [Rachel shouts]
- [hit man grunts]

1297
01:34:05.375 --> 01:34:06.875
[Rachel screams]

1298
01:34:09.000 --> 01:34:10.041
[knife clatters]

1299
01:34:11.541 --> 01:34:12.958
[hit man grunts]

1300
01:34:14.375 --> 01:34:15.500
[both grunting]

1301
01:34:15.583 --> 01:34:16.708
[Rachel shouts]

1302
01:34:20.041 --> 01:34:21.250
[gasps]

1303
01:34:21.958 --> 01:34:23.375
[hit man grunts. panting]

1304
01:34:31.541 --> 01:34:32.916
[muffled screams]

1305
01:34:34.583 --> 01:34:36.000
[hit man continues panting]

1306
01:34:42.166 --> 01:34:44.208
[grunts. exhales]

1307
01:34:44.291 --> 01:34:46.291
[music fading]

1308
01:34:56.250 --> 01:34:57.583
[knife clatters softly]

1309
01:34:58.333 --> 01:34:59.583
[Ray] <i>Come on. baby.</i>

1310
01:35:00.500 --> 01:35:01.500
<i>Get up.</i>

1311
01:35:01.583 --> 01:35:03.458
[hit man continues panting]

1312
01:35:04.958 --> 01:35:07.916
[Ray. emphatically] <i>Get up. sweet girl.</i>

1313
01:35:08.000 --> 01:35:09.416
[suspenseful music playing]

1314
01:35:09.500 --> 01:35:10.666
[Rachel screaming]

1315
01:35:11.458 --> 01:35:12.791
[hit man grunts]

1316
01:35:13.791 --> 01:35:15.333
[both grunting]

1317
01:35:16.083 --> 01:35:17.000
[Rachel yells]

1318
01:35:17.083 --> 01:35:18.333
[hit man screams]

1319
01:35:18.833 --> 01:35:19.958
[Rachel shouts]

1320
01:35:21.500 --> 01:35:22.500
[yells]

1321
01:35:23.750 --> 01:35:24.958
[cries out]

1322
01:35:27.000 --> 01:35:28.000
[knife clatters]

1323
01:35:40.458 --> 01:35:42.625
[music fading]

1324
01:35:42.708 --> 01:35:44.708
[Rachel panting]

1325
01:35:51.625 --> 01:35:53.625
[breathing shakily]

1326
01:36:00.208 --> 01:36:02.208
[rustling]

1327
01:36:07.625 --> 01:36:09.416
[Rachel] Calling the FBI.

1328
01:36:09.500 --> 01:36:10.958
And when they get here.

1329
01:36:11.541 --> 01:36:14.625
you're gonna tell them
everything you did with BioPrime.

1330
01:36:15.625 --> 01:36:18.250
Go ahead. Or better yet. let me.

1331
01:36:19.041 --> 01:36:21.416
I think the FBI is looking for <i>you.</i>

1332
01:36:21.500 --> 01:36:22.500
Rachel.

1333
01:36:22.583 --> 01:36:23.583
[Rachel gasps]

1334
01:36:24.750 --> 01:36:25.750
You know me?

1335
01:36:26.791 --> 01:36:28.375
You're all over the news.

1336
01:36:29.750 --> 01:36:31.000
I've seen what you did.

1337
01:36:31.083 --> 01:36:32.166
[Rachel gasps]

1338
01:36:32.250 --> 01:36:34.125
[Morgan] You bring the FBI here. and…

1339
01:36:35.041 --> 01:36:37.041
Who do you think they're gonna arrest?

1340
01:36:37.875 --> 01:36:40.666
- The crazy girl who killed five men?
- No.

1341
01:36:40.750 --> 01:36:43.833
- [Morgan] Or me?
- No. We never meant to hurt anyone.

1342
01:36:43.916 --> 01:36:46.375
I understand. and I can help you.

1343
01:36:47.250 --> 01:36:49.208
I think I'm the only one who can.

1344
01:36:49.291 --> 01:36:51.416
- I can make this nightmare end.
- Shut up!

1345
01:36:52.208 --> 01:36:56.083
- You're the one behind BioPrime.
- I wrestled them into submission.

1346
01:36:56.166 --> 01:36:59.708
I got them to lower their prices.
Affordable treatment.

1347
01:36:59.791 --> 01:37:01.291
And you cleaned out the rot.

1348
01:37:01.375 --> 01:37:03.291
I'm fighting for <i>you.</i> sweetheart.

1349
01:37:03.375 --> 01:37:04.375
[Rachel grunts]

1350
01:37:04.416 --> 01:37:06.083
[Morgan yells. gasps]

1351
01:37:06.166 --> 01:37:08.541
- [panting]
- [tense music playing]

1352
01:37:09.583 --> 01:37:14.000
When I saw you on CNN
when my mom was in the hospital.

1353
01:37:16.125 --> 01:37:18.291
I thought you could actually save her.

1354
01:37:19.375 --> 01:37:20.833
I believed in you.

1355
01:37:21.458 --> 01:37:23.791
- [shakily] You still can.
- How?

1356
01:37:25.625 --> 01:37:28.583
[inhales sharply]
I know people at the DOJ.

1357
01:37:29.333 --> 01:37:32.041
They can make the charges
against you go away.

1358
01:37:32.666 --> 01:37:34.291
And you can have a life.

1359
01:37:35.916 --> 01:37:40.333
What you've been through.
what happened to you. was wrong. Rachel.

1360
01:37:40.416 --> 01:37:42.416
The trauma you suffered.

1361
01:37:44.833 --> 01:37:47.833
Don't you think they'd want me
to help you. sweetheart?

1362
01:37:47.916 --> 01:37:50.375
- [gasps]
- Stop calling me that.

1363
01:37:50.458 --> 01:37:51.625
You're a liar.

1364
01:37:51.708 --> 01:37:54.083
You were with BioPrime even then.

1365
01:37:54.833 --> 01:37:56.791
You helped them take away

1366
01:37:56.875 --> 01:38:00.083
a cheap and lifesaving
medication for my mom.

1367
01:38:00.166 --> 01:38:02.541
I fought against them! [panting]

1368
01:38:02.625 --> 01:38:06.416
You took their bribe.
and you gave them exclusive contracts.

1369
01:38:06.500 --> 01:38:09.333
<i>You're </i>responsible
for ordering the hit on Martin Bennett.

1370
01:38:09.416 --> 01:38:11.750
You killed my dad.

1371
01:38:11.833 --> 01:38:13.458
[softly] Now tell the truth.

1372
01:38:14.583 --> 01:38:16.916
- [Morgan gasps]
- [firmly] Tell me the truth.

1373
01:38:18.208 --> 01:38:19.208
[Morgan sighs]

1374
01:38:20.041 --> 01:38:21.083
[scoffs]

1375
01:38:21.583 --> 01:38:22.583
Yeah.

1376
01:38:22.625 --> 01:38:24.791
[tense music playing]

1377
01:38:24.875 --> 01:38:26.500
I took the bribe.

1378
01:38:30.958 --> 01:38:31.958
I ordered the hit.

1379
01:38:33.250 --> 01:38:34.291
[chuckles softly]

1380
01:38:35.916 --> 01:38:38.583
You don't understand anything.
You're so young.

1381
01:38:38.666 --> 01:38:40.583
[laughs]

1382
01:38:40.666 --> 01:38:43.833
The candidate with the most money wins.

1383
01:38:45.291 --> 01:38:47.000
That's how it works.

1384
01:38:47.083 --> 01:38:49.083
[Rachel breathing shakily]

1385
01:38:49.166 --> 01:38:51.166
[tense music building]

1386
01:38:52.583 --> 01:38:53.916
Was it worth it?

1387
01:38:56.208 --> 01:38:57.708
Was it worth it?

1388
01:38:57.791 --> 01:38:59.000
[Morgan groans softly]

1389
01:39:03.833 --> 01:39:04.833
[Rachel sobs softly]

1390
01:39:15.833 --> 01:39:17.875
[music fades]

1391
01:39:20.833 --> 01:39:21.833
[Morgan gasps]

1392
01:39:22.583 --> 01:39:24.041
[breathing shakily]

1393
01:39:27.125 --> 01:39:28.166
Security?

1394
01:39:29.541 --> 01:39:30.708
[takes a deep breath]

1395
01:39:31.208 --> 01:39:33.291
[yelling] Security!

1396
01:39:38.458 --> 01:39:40.041
[Rachel panting]

1397
01:39:47.750 --> 01:39:50.583
- [somber music playing]
- [sirens wailing in distance]

1398
01:39:53.916 --> 01:39:55.375
[tires squealing]

1399
01:39:57.083 --> 01:39:59.083
[indistinct chatter]

1400
01:40:06.500 --> 01:40:07.500
[Rachel groaning]

1401
01:40:14.166 --> 01:40:18.125
She kills Keeley and runs.
Tries to escape. but something or someone

1402
01:40:18.208 --> 01:40:20.500
drove her back here.
despite knowing she might be caught.

1403
01:40:20.583 --> 01:40:23.208
[Rothman] Yeah. but she got
her revenge. Why come back?

1404
01:40:23.291 --> 01:40:24.916
- [agent] Just came in.
- Thank you. sir.

1405
01:40:25.000 --> 01:40:26.125
[agent] You're welcome.

1406
01:40:28.375 --> 01:40:30.125
- Holy shit.
- [Meeker] What?

1407
01:40:33.291 --> 01:40:35.166
[Rothman] <i>Rachel Cooper was spotted</i>

1408
01:40:35.250 --> 01:40:38.000
<i>at Diana Morgan's campaign rally
yesterday afternoon.</i>

1409
01:40:39.583 --> 01:40:41.250
[Meeker] <i>What was she doing there?</i>

1410
01:40:44.333 --> 01:40:47.458
[reporter on TV] <i>The fugitive</i>
<i>from last night's assassination attempt</i>…

1411
01:40:47.541 --> 01:40:48.416
[Rachel] Thanks.

1412
01:40:48.500 --> 01:40:50.208
<i>…on Diana Morgan is still on the loose.</i>

1413
01:40:50.291 --> 01:40:52.750
<i>Pittsburgh police are asking
anyone with information</i>

1414
01:40:52.833 --> 01:40:54.291
<i>to please come forward.</i>

1415
01:40:54.375 --> 01:40:57.125
[Rothman] <i>First Keeley.</i>
<i>then Shah. now a congresswoman?</i>

1416
01:40:58.333 --> 01:41:00.000
<i>It just seems so bizarre.</i>

1417
01:41:00.750 --> 01:41:02.750
[Meeker] <i>Rachel clearly knows something.</i>

1418
01:41:04.166 --> 01:41:07.125
<i>Let's go through Diana Morgan's
campaign donations.</i>

1419
01:41:07.750 --> 01:41:08.833
[cell phone chimes]

1420
01:41:08.916 --> 01:41:10.083
[computer alert chimes]

1421
01:41:12.791 --> 01:41:15.750
[Meeker] Look at this.
Rachel Cooper just sent us something.

1422
01:41:18.875 --> 01:41:22.708
[Morgan on recording]
<i>I took the bribe. I ordered the hit.</i>

1423
01:41:24.041 --> 01:41:27.166
<i>The candidate with the most money wins.</i>

1424
01:41:28.583 --> 01:41:29.583
<i>That's how it works.</i>

1425
01:41:29.666 --> 01:41:32.666
[reporter on TV] <i>…developments</i>
<i>in the assassination attempt.</i>

1426
01:41:32.750 --> 01:41:36.083
<i>According to sources.
the FBI has arrested the congresswoman</i>

1427
01:41:36.166 --> 01:41:37.333
<i>regarding her connection</i>

1428
01:41:37.416 --> 01:41:39.458
<i>to the recent murders
of BioPrime executives</i>

1429
01:41:39.541 --> 01:41:41.666
<i>Simon Keeley and Vinod Shah</i>

1430
01:41:41.750 --> 01:41:45.916
<i>and the two-year-old unsolved murders
of Martin Bennett and Ray Cooper.</i>

1431
01:41:46.000 --> 01:41:50.416
<i>Neither BioPrime or the FBI would
comment on this ongoing investigation.</i>

1432
01:41:50.500 --> 01:41:51.708
[soaring music playing]

1433
01:41:51.791 --> 01:41:55.875
<i>…Pennsylvania is allegedly connected
to the deaths of reporter Martin Bennett</i>

1434
01:41:55.958 --> 01:41:58.875
<i>and Rachel Cooper's father
nearly two years ago.</i>

1435
01:41:58.958 --> 01:42:00.708
[Ray] <i>The past is like a dream.</i>

1436
01:42:02.208 --> 01:42:05.166
<i>A mosaic of images and feelings</i>

1437
01:42:05.250 --> 01:42:07.791
<i>that offers some truth
about how we got here.</i>

1438
01:42:07.875 --> 01:42:10.291
<i>even if details have blurred with time.</i>

1439
01:42:12.458 --> 01:42:14.291
<i>Parents and their children.</i>

1440
01:42:15.125 --> 01:42:16.458
<i>Where do we stop…</i>

1441
01:42:17.458 --> 01:42:18.916
[Rachel] <i>…and they begin?</i>

1442
01:42:24.375 --> 01:42:27.125
{\an8}[instrumental music continues playing]

1443
01:45:37.791 --> 01:45:40.541
[somber instrumental music playing]

